    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>Corrections</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of July 10 article on report by Investor Responsibility Research Center on companies' preparations for business effects of global warming regarding given name of report's author and center's executive director</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>An article in Business Day yesterday about a report by the Investor Responsibility Research Center in Washington on companies' preparations for the business effects of global warming misstated the given name of the main author and the surname of the center's executive director. The author is Douglas G. Cogan, not Dan. The executive director is Mindy Lubber, not Luber.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>An article in Business Day yesterday about a report by the Investor Responsibility Research Center in Washington on companies' preparations for the business effects of global warming misstated the given name of the main author and the surname of the center's executive director. The author is Douglas G. Cogan, not Dan. The executive director is Mindy Lubber, not Luber.</p>
